# Public client env. Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) — or `.env` since the
# value is public. VITE_ vars are embedded into the built JS at build time, so
# only put NON-secret values here, and rebuild after changing them.

# Cloudflare Turnstile SITE key (public). Pairs with TURNSTILE_SECRET in
# .dev.vars. When unset, the in-app "Request a park" form shows as unavailable.
# For local testing, Cloudflare's always-passes test site key works:
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=1x00000000000000000000AA
